What you need to know:

Keeping dairy goats in urban areas is advantageous because the price of milk is higher and the farmer is near the targeted market.In urban areas, you can also become a breeder by selling to people buying to keep the animals in rural areas.Recently, the Nairobi County Assembly developed standards for livestock keeping in the city.Â In the draft bylaws, to keep sheep or goats in the city, one needs to be registered and the sheds and pens certified.